In conclusion, I express my deepest remorse and take full responsibility for my actions as I plead guilty to the charge of being drunk and disorderly. I understand the harm caused by my behavior and genuinely seek to rectify the situation. I ask for the court's leniency and guidance in determining a suitable course of action that will allow me to demonstrate my commitment to personal growth, accountability, and responsible behavior.

Thank you for your attention to this matter.

